      "content": "{\"parentUuid\":null,\"isSidechain\":true,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/opt/development/clooks\",\"sessionId\":\"846423a7-b4c9-4a4e-ac08-b2f0d0b0dd9d\",\"version\":\"2.1.72\",\"gitBranch\":\"master\",\"agentId\":\"a26cf582658a09f6f\",\"type\":\"user\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Research the Claude Code hooks documentation at https://code.claude.com/docs/en/hooks#json-output\\n\\nWe're investigating which hook events actually fire in Claude Code and their expected behavior. Specifically:\\n\\n1. Do SubagentStart/SubagentStop events actually fire? When?\\n2. Do TeammateIdle/TaskCompleted events actually fire? When?\\n3. Does Stop fire at the end of every turn?\\n4. Does ConfigChange fire when settings files are edited?\\n5. Does InstructionsLoaded fire when skills are loaded?\\n6. Does PermissionRequest fire and under what conditions?\\n7. How does the hook output work for events that fire outside tool calls (like Stop, ConfigChange)?\\n\\nAlso check https://code.claude.com/docs/en/hooks for the main hooks page.\\n\\nReport everything you find about these events, especially whether they're documented as implemented or just planned/spec.\"},\"uuid\":\"b4026664-dd1c-4365-92e1-f91d215bb6e7\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-11T16:56:27.771Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"8e055fa5-feea-4355-a69e-be8e986b49de\",\"isSidechain\":true,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/opt/development/clooks\",\"sessionId\":\"846423a7-b4c9-4a4e-ac08-b2f0d0b0dd9d\",\"version\":\"2.1.72\",\"gitBranch\":\"master\",\"agentId\":\"a26cf582658a09f6f\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01STutXbN8YvVrcEchsaXV4z\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\nI'll fetch both documentation pages to research the hook events.\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":11563,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_t